aruna-prasad.content: Aruna is a freshman in the Jerome Fisher Program in Management and Technology studying Computer Science and Finance. Besides Hack4Impact, Aruna is involved in Wharton Analytics Fellows, the Wharton Customer Analytics Initiative and research. In high school, Aruna founded Nerdina, an inter-school non-profit where girls build circuits and learn about how the technology around them works.
